      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      interface  NewRakNetOnly
      Indicates that the annotated element is only available in PowerNukkit or in Cloudburst Nukkit environment with the "new-raknet" branch merged and will cause issues when used in a normal Nukkit server without the "new-raknet" patches and features.
      interface  PowerNukkitDifference
      Indicates that the annotated element works differently in PowerNukkit environment and may cause issues or unexpected behaviour when used in a normal NukkitX server without PowerNukkit's patches and features.
      static interface  PowerNukkitDifference.DifferenceList 
      interface  PowerNukkitOnly
      Indicates that the annotated element is only available in PowerNukkit environment and will cause issues when used in a normal NukkitX server without PowerNukkit's patches and features.
      interface  RemovedFromNewRakNet
      Indicates that the annotated element was removed in the popular Cloudburst new-raknet branch, using it will work in PowerNukkit and normal Nukkit but will cause issues in that branch or when the branch gets merged.
      interface  Unsigned
      Indicates that the number may be negative in raw form but must be treated as an unsigned value by considering the sign bit as part of the number.
